	<h2>About David Rhoderick</h2>
	<p>David is <?php echo date( 'Y-m-d' ) - "1988-08-26"; ?> years old. He is currently a graduate student studying at the School of Visual Arts in New York for a Computer Art MFA degree.  He started as a self-produced musician and eventually became a broadcast video producer and camera operator.  Today, his work is characterized by use of code to experiment with both automation and data manipulation in pieces that attempt to take a pragmatic approach to our relationship to our environments as facilitated through our consciousness.</p>